data.description: This inviting 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home offers ample space for gatherings and boasts an airy layout that's sure to charm you. With stunning wood floors gracing the living room and master bedroom, comfort meets elegance throughout. The secondary rooms feature cozy carpeting, providing a warm touch. The master bath is your very own spa retreat with a soaking tub, separate shower and walk in closets. Plus, enjoy the convenience of a sprinkler system, lush sod, and a 6-foot cedar privacy fence. Stunning community pool and bike-walking trail. Conveniently located just minutes from Wylie High School.
